CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 23, 1951, pg. 6 reads: "Contestants - The six college students pictured above are among the nine students who are vying for scholarships from the Metoka Club. Winners of the contest will be announced at the annual garden party sponsored by Metoka Club on July 19. Lower row: ...Myron Ta..."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Myron T., wearing necktie and houndstooth suit jacket, posed in front of light colored backdrop in Harris Studio
